## 📌 Project Overview

This project implements a **Content-Based Recommendation System** that matches user skills with relevant tech job roles. Unlike collaborative filtering (which relies on other users' behavior), this system focuses on matching user preferences directly to item attributes.

### Project Goal
Create a simple recommendation system based on user preferences using similarity matching and vector space models.

